snippet.title: Quick Tops
snippet.description:
Hey Guys! On this channel we make Top 10's, Top 5's, Tv Show Recaps, Movie and TV Show Theories and more. We made this channel where we do our best to make Top 10's faster to watch and easier to understand.

Check out our Twitter.
https://twitter.com/QuickTops

Check out our Channel on Dailymotion if you prefer it over YouTube.
http://www.dailymotion.com/QuickTops

Check out our Second Channel - QuickTops Two.
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC7BIQBUHm1TMtDotOFG2OKw

Feel free to look at our books and purchase some if you are feeling adventurous!
https://www.amazon.com/dp/B079YGMJH1 - 1000+ Facts About Your Favorite Hollywood Actors
https://www.amazon.com/dp/B07K5DY9T2 - 1000+ Facts About Your Favorite Hollywood Actresses
